# Cloud Functions environment — copy to functions/.env (gitignored) and fill in.
# These drive server-side role assignment in the ensureProfile function, so the
# allowlist is NEVER shipped in the client bundle.
#
# Comma-separated email lists. An email in SUPERADMIN_EMAILS becomes
# 'superadmin' (Administrator); ADMIN_EMAILS becomes 'admin' (Manager);
# everyone else is 'user'. Everyone else must be pre-registered via the Team
# page to sign in at all.

SUPERADMIN_EMAILS=
ADMIN_EMAILS=
